<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1803745-anyone-write-me-back-please-i-m-looking">Anyone write me back please! 
I&#39;m looking for a book quite like this, but set in historical Western. A girl is out for revenge for her sister who has supposedly been &#39;deflowered&#39; by a cowboy.She spikes the drink of a guy in a salon thinking it to be him. She instead gets the older brother and is forced into marriage with him. They end up falling in love. Anyone please?</a>
</div>
