        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4127431604" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7660581969049397818">Another good story about the MacCarrick. This is Ethan and Maddy rocky romance. Ethen is brutally beaten and left with a horrible scar on his face. He takes his revenge and Maddy is caught up in it. Needed a tissue near the end of this story.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


